<item>
            <title>[PIG-923] Allow setting logfile location in pig.properties</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-923</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Local log file location can be specified through the -l flag, but it cannot be set in pig.properties.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This JIRA proposes a change to Main.java that allows it to read the &quot;pig.logfile&quot; property from the configuration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
