                            <comment id="12743363" author="dvryaboy" created="Fri, 14 Aug 2009 18:56:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One-line change to allow Main.java to default to the value specified in pig.logfile.&lt;br/&gt;
-l still overrides.&lt;br/&gt;
Not specifying pig.logfile in pig.properties results in the same behavior as before.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No unit tests; checked manually.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
